---
title: Roasted Pepper Cavatappi Milano with Fresh Mozzarella & Basil
description: No matter the weather, it’s impossible not to daydream about a bubbly, soul-warming pasta dish. Well, folks, that dream is now a reality. This delicious dish has curly cavatappi and tender strips of roasted bell pepper cloaked in a creamy tomato-basil sauce. It’s topped off with fresh mozzarella and panko breadcrumbs before being broiled to gooey, golden-brown perfection. Yep, this one-pan wonder is guaranteed to satisfy all carby cravings. (We’re all about making dreams come true.)
